{"title":"ES6 陣列解構與強化","uid":"99ccec2fc965b4adf661053ed0649d5f","slug":"ES6 陣列解構與強化","date":"2021-03-15T16:00:00.000Z","updated":"2022-08-01T18:29:03.461Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/ES6 陣列解構與強化.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":"<h1 id=\"ES6-陣列解構與強化\"><a href=\"#ES6-陣列解構與強化\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"ES6 陣列解構與強化\"></a>ES6 陣列解構與強化</h1><p>陣列同樣也有解構賦值的寫法，本次讀書會使用到的 React Hooks 也經常被使用。</p>\n<h2 id=\"陣列解構\"><a href=\"#陣列解構\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"陣列解構\"></a>陣列解構</h2><p>以前我們要讀取陣列裡面的值，都會使用如下程式碼來取值：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-javascript\" data-language=\"javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">const family &#x3D; [&quot;爸&quot;, &quot;媽&quot;, &quot;姊姊&quot;, &quot;哥哥&quot;];\n\n&#x2F;&#x2F; 一般會這樣寫\nconst papa &#x3D; family[0];\nconst mama &#x3D; family[1];\nconst sister &#x3D; family[2];\nconst brother &#x3D; family[3];</code></pre>\n\n<p>但藉由 ES6 的<code>陣列解構</code>語法，下方程式碼也可達到一樣效果，讓程式碼可以更精簡：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-javascript\" data-language=\"javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">const family &#x3D; [&quot;爸&quot;, &quot;媽&quot;, &quot;姊姊&quot;, &quot;哥哥&quot;];\n\n&#x2F;&#x2F; 縮寫版\nconst [papa, mama, sister, brother] &#x3D; family;\n\nconsole.log(papa); &#x2F;&#x2F; &#39;爸爸&#39;\nconsole.log(sister); &#x2F;&#x2F; &#39;姊姊&#39;</code></pre>\n\n<p>若是遇到空的變數，會將值跳過</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-javascript\" data-language=\"javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">const family &#x3D; [&quot;爸&quot;, &quot;媽&quot;, &quot;姊姊&quot;, &quot;哥哥&quot;];\nconst [papa, , , brother] &#x3D; family;\n\nconsole.log(papa); &#x2F;&#x2F; &#39;爸爸&#39;\nconsole.log(brother); &#x2F;&#x2F; &#39;哥哥&#39;</code></pre>\n\n<p>若是左邊的變數數量多餘右邊的值，會將多出來的變數賦予 <code>undefined</code></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-javascript\" data-language=\"javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">const family &#x3D; [&quot;爸&quot;, &quot;媽&quot;, &quot;姊姊&quot;, &quot;哥哥&quot;];\nconst [papa, , , brother, grandpa] &#x3D; family; &#x2F;&#x2F; 有五個變數\n\nconsole.log(papa); &#x2F;&#x2F; &#39;爸爸&#39;\nconsole.log(brother); &#x2F;&#x2F; &#39;哥哥&#39;\nconsole.log(grandpa); &#x2F;&#x2F; undefined</code></pre>\n\n<p>若是值為<strong>字串</strong>，會將字串拆解為一個一個字元</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-javascript\" data-language=\"javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">const family &#x3D; &quot;family&quot;;\nconst [papa, , , brother, grandpa] &#x3D; family;\n\nconsole.log(papa); &#x2F;&#x2F; &#39;f&#39;\nconsole.log(brother); &#x2F;&#x2F; &#39;i&#39;\nconsole.log(grandpa); &#x2F;&#x2F; &#39;l&#39;</code></pre>\n\n<p><strong>可以輕易互換變數</strong></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-javascript\" data-language=\"javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">let papa &#x3D; &quot;爸爸&quot;;\nlet mama &#x3D; &quot;媽媽&quot;;\n\n[papa, mama] &#x3D; [mama, papa];\n\nconsole.log(papa); &#x2F;&#x2F; &#39;媽媽&#39;\nconsole.log(mama); &#x2F;&#x2F; &#39;爸爸&#39;</code></pre>\n\n<h2 id=\"Demo\"><a href=\"#Demo\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Demo\"></a>Demo</h2><ol>\n<li><p>優化下方將陣列內的值賦予到變數上的寫法</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-javascript\" data-language=\"javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">&#x2F;&#x2F; 舊寫法\nconst students &#x3D; [&quot;安妮&quot;, &quot;露璐&quot;, &quot;努努&quot;, &quot;索娜&quot;, &quot;艾希&quot;];\nconst lulu &#x3D; students[1];\nconst nunu &#x3D; students[2];\nconst ashe &#x3D; students[4];\n\n&#x2F;&#x2F; 新寫法\nconst [, lulu, nunu, , ashe] &#x3D; students;\nconsole.log(lulu);\nconsole.log(nunu);</code></pre>\n</li>\n<li><p>運用陣列解構賦值，將下方 numbers 變數內 1 和 5 對調，變為 <code>[5, 7, 1]</code></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-javascript\" data-language=\"javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">&#x2F;&#x2F; 新寫法\nlet numbers &#x3D; [1, 7, 5];\n[numbers[0], numbers[1], numbers[2]] &#x3D; [numbers[2], numbers[1], numbers[0]];\nconsole.log(numbers);</code></pre></li>\n</ol>\n","text":"ES6 陣列解構與強化陣列同樣也有解構賦值的寫法，本次讀書會使用到的 React Hooks 也經常被使用。 陣列解構以前我們要讀取陣列裡面的值，都會使用如下程式碼來取值： const family &#x3D; [&quot;爸&quot;, &quot;媽&quot;, &q...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"2.2k","symbolsTime":"2 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"JavaScript","slug":"JavaScript","count":45,"path":"api/categories/JavaScript.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"JavaScript","slug":"JavaScript","count":39,"path":"api/tags/JavaScript.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#ES6-%E9%99%A3%E5%88%97%E8%A7%A3%E6%A7%8B%E8%88%87%E5%BC%B7%E5%8C%96\"><span class=\"toc-text\">ES6 陣列解構與強化</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E9%99%A3%E5%88%97%E8%A7%A3%E6%A7%8B\"><span class=\"toc-text\">陣列解構</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Demo\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Demo</span></a></li></ol></li></ol>","author":{"name":"Michael","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210313122054101.png","link":"/","description":"happy coding!","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/Michael0520","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{"title":"(Project) Speak Number Guessing Game","uid":"389702db6779280e4f383b25bb2a6513","slug":"Speak Number Guessing Game","date":"2021-03-16T16:00:00.000Z","updated":"2022-06-13T13:59:22.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Speak Number Guessing Game.json","keywords":null,"cover":[],"text":"學習到的知識點CSS display:inline-block JS html() 完全替代 &amp; append() 新增追加 Web Speech API 簡介猜數字遊戲Demo HTML結構 &lt;img src&#x3D;&quot;.&#x2F;img&#x2F;...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"8.8k","symbolsTime":"8 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"JavaScript","slug":"JavaScript","count":45,"path":"api/categories/JavaScript.json"},{"name":"作品集","slug":"JavaScript/作品集","count":18,"path":"api/categories/JavaScript/作品集.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"JavaScript","slug":"JavaScript","count":39,"pat